SUMMARY:University of Freiburg Open Science mini-conference. The focus of the meeting will be on theory development and its intersections with Open Science. Invited speakers: Prof. Daniel Lakens (Technical University Eindhoven, Netherlands), Dr. Priya Silverstein (Ashland University & Psychological Science Accelerator, USA), Freek Oude Maatman (University of Groningen & Radboud University Nijmegen, Netherlands), Sajedeh Rasti (Technical University Eindhoven, Netherlands).
